		<Section title='Experience'>
			<Card
				heading='Senior Smart Contract Engineer'
				subheading='Euler Labs'
				date='Nov 2023 - Present'
				imagePath='/src/assets/about-astro.png'
				altText='Euler Labs logo'
				imageClass='h-12 w-auto md:-left-16'
			>
				<ul class='ml-4 list-disc text-muted-foreground'>
					<li>Designing and writing technical spec for a modular DEX protocol.</li>
					<li>Researching AMM designs.</li>
					<li>Contributing in a modular lending protocol implementation,
						mainly writing tests and doing security code reviews.</li>
					<li>Contributing in improving the engineering and development processes.</li>
				</ul>
			</Card>
			<Card
				heading='Senior Smart Contract Engineer'
				subheading='Opyn'
				date='Apr 2020 - Nov 2023'
				imagePath='/src/assets/about-astro.png'
				altText='Opyn logo'
				imageClass='h-12 w-auto md:-left-16'
			>
				<ul class='ml-4 list-disc text-muted-foreground'>
					<li>Designing and writing technical specs for on-chain options, derivatives protocol, yield strategies, oracles contracts.</li>
